---
layout: layouts/base
title: Tags
description: Browse every topic on Chris Hannah's blog by tag.
permalink: /tags/
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<h1 class="page-title">Tags</h1>
<p class="intro-text">Browse {{ collections.tagList | length }} topics from across the archive, most-used first.</p>

<div class="tag-cloud">
  {% for tag in collections.tagList %}
  <a class="tag-cloud-item" href="/tags/{{ tag.slug }}/">{{ tag.label }}<span class="tag-count">{{ tag.count }}</span></a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
